project_descr:
Restoration of disrupted livelihoods of affected residents and displaced
people including returnees in East Aleppo through rehabilitation of basic
services and revival of local businesses and affected vocational workshops.

outputs.output_descr:
Provision of socio-economic support including vocational training and distribution of productive assets to affected market and vocational
workshops in the industrial zone in the project target areas (Kallaseh, Bostan Al Qaser, and Al Sha’ar)
